<bibRefCitation author="Chen" box="[924,1147,1573,1601]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Chen" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" pagination="3951 - 3978" refId="ref33869" refString="Chen, H. W., Gao, J. J. &amp; Wen, S. Y. (2005 a) Species diversity of the genus Phortica Schiner in Yunnan, China, with descriptions of nine new species (Diptera, Drosophildae [sic]). Journal of Natural History, 39, 3951 - 3978. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222930500533534" type="journal article" year="2005" yearSuffix="a">
